fields.label: Hazard
fields.description: Hazard: Harm to people, property or the environment

fields.label: Hazardous situation (cause of harm)
fields.description: Circumstances in which people, property or the environment are exposed to one or more hazards

fields.label: Harm (effect of the failure)
fields.description: Physical injury or damage to the health of people, or damage to property or the environment

fields.label: Risk Color (Color)
fields.title: Color
fields.formula:
customField[4]*customField[5] > 0 and customField[4]*customField[5] <= 18? "%%(color:#00a85d;)█%!": (
customField[4]*customField[5] > 18 and customField[4]*customField[5] <= 48 ? "%%(color:#ffab46;)█%!" : (
customField[4]*customField[5] > 48 and customField[4]*customField[5] <= 100 ?  "%%(color:#b31317;)█%!" : 
"%%(color:#ffff;)█%!"))

fields.label: Severity after risk reduction (S')
fields.title: S'
fields.description: Severity typically does not change due to mitigation. If the severity changed, please explain in Risk Comment.

fields.label: Reduced Risk Color (Color')
fields.title: Color'
fields.formula:
customField[8]*customField[9] > 0 and customField[8]*customField[9] <= 18? "%%(color:#00a85d;)█%!": (
customField[8]*customField[9] > 18 and customField[8]*customField[9] <= 48 ? "%%(color:#ffab46;)█%!" : (
customField[8]*customField[9] > 48 and customField[8]*customField[9] <= 100 ?  "%%(color:#b31317;)█%!" : 
"%%(color:#ffff;)█%!"))
